You added `inputBar` to the `root` BorderPane twice.

I don’t advise adding to the children of a border pane directly either.  Instead, use the positional setters on the borderPane to set the positions of the children (those setters will internally add the set nodes as children).  Study the [`BorderPane`](https://openjfx.io/javadoc/19/javafx.graphics/javafx/scene/layout/BorderPane.html) documentation.

